    public long countAlternatingSubarrays(int[] nums) {
        long sum = 0;
        int n = nums.length;
        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (i > 0 && nums[i - 1] == nums[i]) {
                sum += count * (count + 1) / 2;
                count = 1;
            } else {
                count++;
            }
        }
        if (count != 0) {
            sum += count * (count + 1) / 2;
        }
        return sum;
    }
}
